study_title: Distribution and clinical impact of functional variants in 50,726 whole-exome sequences from the DiscovEHR study. Science
description: For each variant seen in dicoverEHR we kept info about the allele frequency (AF). AF < 0.001 are binned together and reported as AF = 0.001.

nodes.description: Allele Frequency in discovEHR. AF=0.001 is equal to AF<=0.001
